{"title":"从“五四”想到“四五”","authors":["王为政"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":5,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"从“五四”想到“四五”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王为政"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从“五四”想到“四五”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——相隔五十七年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发生在同一国度。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头上，同一片赤县天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚下，同一块神州土。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同是一群轩辕子孙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为“中华腾飞于世界”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢“问苍茫大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁主沉浮？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史竟这样惊人地相似，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同样的字体记载着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“五四”——“四五”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不！不！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史决不只是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"简单的重复。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年，人民还未“降龙”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今，中国却已“伏虎”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史，翻过了五十七年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民，已经更加成熟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当窃国大盗再一次磨牙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门前又升起冲天烟柱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国是人民的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民就要作主！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"君不见自古“民不畏死”？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了“庶民的胜利”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了“四化”宏图——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要时时想起："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“五四”——“四五”……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}